{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"9071","heading":"Milk donation program","label":"9071 Milk donation program","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch115/schIII/ptB","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsA prior section 9071, , , , related to dairy product donation program, prior to repeal by , , .Pub. L. 113–79, title I, § 1431128 Stat. 695Pub. L. 115–334, title I, § 1404(a)132 Stat. 4519Feb. 7, 2014Dec. 20, 2018"],"amendments":["Prior ProvisionsA prior section 9071, , , , related to dairy product donation program, prior to repeal by , , .Pub. L. 113–79, title I, § 1431128 Stat. 695Pub. L. 115–334, title I, § 1404(a)132 Stat. 4519Feb. 7, 2014Dec. 20, 2018"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definitions","label":"a Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Eligible dairy organization","label":"1 Eligible dairy organization","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"accounts to a Federal milk marketing order marketwide pool; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"incurs qualified expenses under subsection (e).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Eligible distributor","label":"2 Eligible distributor","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “eligible distributor” means a public or private nonprofit organization that distributes donated eligible milk.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Eligible milk","label":"3 Eligible milk","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “eligible milk” means Class I fluid milk products produced and processed in the United States.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Eligible partnership","label":"4 Eligible partnership","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “eligible partnership” means a partnership between an eligible dairy organization and an eligible distributor.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Participating partnership","label":"5 Participating partnership","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “participating partnership” means an eligible partnership for which the Secretary has approved a donation and distribution plan for eligible milk under subsection (c)(2).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Program required; purposes","label":"b Program required; purposes","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"encouraging the donation of eligible milk;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"providing nutrition assistance to individuals in low-income groups; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"reducing food waste.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Donation and distribution plans","label":"c Donation and distribution plans","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"describes the process that the eligible partnership will use for the donation, processing, transportation, temporary storage, and distribution of eligible milk;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"preplanned donations; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"contingency plans to address unanticipated donations; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"describes the rate at which the eligible partnership will be reimbursed, which shall be based on a percentage of the limitation described in subsection (e)(2), not to exceed 100 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Review and approval","label":"2 Review and approval","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"review donation and distribution plans submitted under paragraph (1); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"determine whether to approve or disapprove each of those donation and distribution plans.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Reimbursement","label":"d Reimbursement","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"On receipt of appropriate documentation under paragraph (2), the Secretary shall reimburse an eligible dairy organization that is a member of a participating partnership on a regular basis for qualified expenses described in subsection (e).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Documentation","label":"2 Documentation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An eligible dairy organization shall submit to the Secretary such documentation as the Secretary may require to demonstrate the qualified expenses described in subsection (e) of the eligible dairy organization.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Verification","label":"B Verification","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary may verify the accuracy of documentation submitted under subparagraph (A) by spot checks and audits.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Retroactive reimbursement","label":"3 Retroactive reimbursement","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In providing reimbursements under paragraph (1), the Secretary may provide reimbursements for qualified expenses incurred before the date on which the donation and distribution plan for the applicable participating partnership was approved by the Secretary.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Qualified expenses","label":"e Qualified expenses","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fe%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the quantity of eligible milk donated by the eligible dairy organization under a donation and distribution plan approved by the Secretary under subsection (c); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fe%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"subject to the limitation under paragraph (2), the rate described in that donation and distribution plan under subsection (c)(1)(C).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Limitation","label":"2 Limitation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Expenses eligible for reimbursement under subsection (d) shall not exceed the value that an eligible dairy organization incurred by accounting to the Federal milk marketing order pool at the difference in the Class I milk value and the lowest classified price for the applicable month (either Class III milk or Class IV milk).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Preapproval","label":"f Preapproval","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish a process for an eligible partnership to apply for preapproval of donation and distribution plans under subsection (c); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the feasibility of the plan; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the extent to which the plan advances the purposes described in subsection (b).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Preference","label":"2 Preference","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In preapproving amounts for reimbursement under paragraph (1)(B), the Secretary shall give preference to eligible partnerships that will provide funding and in-kind contributions in addition to the reimbursements.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Adjustments","label":"3 Adjustments","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall adjust or increase amounts preapproved for reimbursement under paragraph (1)(B) based on performance and demand.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Requests for increase","label":"B Requests for increase","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":"In general","label":"i In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall establish a procedure for a participating partnership to request an increase in the amount preapproved for reimbursement under paragraph (1)(B) based on changes in conditions.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":"Interim approval; incremental increase","label":"ii Interim approval; incremental increase","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/f/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Ff%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary may provide an interim approval of an increase requested under clause (i) and an incremental increase in the amount of reimbursement to the applicable participating partnership to allow time for the Secretary to review the request without interfering with the donation and distribution of eligible milk by the participating partnership.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":"Prohibition on resale of products","label":"g Prohibition on resale of products","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/g/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fg%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An eligible distributor that receives eligible milk donated under this section may not sell the products back into commercial markets.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Prohibition on future participation","label":"2 Prohibition on future participation","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/g/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fg%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An eligible distributor that the Secretary determines has violated paragraph (1) shall not be eligible for any future participation in the program established under this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"h","heading":"Administration","label":"h Administration","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/h","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fh","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall publicize opportunities to participate in the program established under this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"i","heading":"Reviews","label":"i Reviews","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall conduct appropriate reviews or audits to ensure the integrity of the program established under this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"j","heading":"Funding","label":"j Funding","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071/j","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s9071","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs9071%2Fj","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Of the funds of the Commodity Credit Corporation, the Secretary shall use to carry out this section $9,000,000 for fiscal year 2019, and $5,000,000 for each fiscal year thereafter, to remain available until expended.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
